text: Istis autem circumdatus est terminibus locus qui dicitur Plyssche.
Erest on Ruanberghe þanne on stanwey.
Þanne on an hul to hamme.
Þanen on an welle up on brugh doune on warrode þanen on windberghes.
Þanen endlang herepathes on þar weilete.
Þanen over thorncombe on anne crundil.
Þanen west over Plisshe on an Sticholnelniche.
Þanen over whetecombe on alden doune op bi wirtrone on an ruwe dich.
Þannen adoun over yfre þanen out on bromhulle of bromhulle eft on Ruanberghe.
